<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>University Life | Open Day</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <!-- AOS for scroll animations -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    {% include 'index1.twig' %}
    <main class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <section class="content-section bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 p-md-5">
                <h1 class="mb-4 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">University Life at Wolverhampton</h1>
                <p class="lead mb-5 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Experience the vibrant community and rich opportunities at the University of Wolverhampton.</p>
                
                <!-- Main sections -->
                <div class="row g-4 mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <!-- Learning Environment -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <div class="icon-box bg-light rounded-circle me-3">
                                        <i class="bi bi-book text-primary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="h4 mb-0">Learning Environment</h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-0">Our students enjoy modern lecture theaters, state-of-the-art laboratories, and extensive library resources. The Harrison Learning Centre provides 24/7 study spaces, IT facilities, and quiet zones for individual work.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Student Community -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <div class="icon-box bg-light rounded-circle me-3">
                                        <i class="bi bi-people text-primary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="h4 mb-0">Student Community</h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-0">Join a diverse community of students from over 120 countries. Our Student Union offers numerous clubs, societies, and events throughout the year, from cultural festivals to sports competitions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Campus Life -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <div class="icon-box bg-light rounded-circle me-3">
                                        <i class="bi bi-building text-primary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="h4 mb-0">Campus Facilities</h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-0">Our Wolverhampton campuses feature modern sports facilities, including the University gym, swimming pool, and sports hall. The student-friendly spaces include cafeterias, common rooms, and study areas.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- City Integration -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <div class="icon-box bg-light rounded-circle me-3">
                                        <i class="bi bi-geo-alt text-primary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="h4 mb-0">City Integration</h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-0">Located in the heart of Wolverhampton, students enjoy easy access to the city centre's shops, restaurants, and entertainment venues. The Mander Shopping Centre and historic Grand Theatre are just minutes away.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Support Services -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <div class="icon-box bg-light rounded-circle me-3">
                                        <i class="bi bi-heart text-primary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="h4 mb-0">Student Support</h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-0">Access comprehensive support services including academic advisors, counselling, disability support, and financial guidance. Our student mentors and peer support networks help you settle into university life.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Cultural Life -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <div class="icon-box bg-light rounded-circle me-3">
                                        <i class="bi bi-palette text-primary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="h4 mb-0">Cultural Life</h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-0">Experience Wolverhampton's rich cultural scene with regular exhibitions, performances, and cultural events. The University actively participates in city festivals and maintains strong ties with local cultural institutions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- A Day in the Life -->
                <div class="mt-5 mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">A Day in the Life of a Student</h2>
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                            <img src="images/student1.jpg" alt="Student life" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="timeline">
                                <div class="timeline-item mb-3 position-relative ps-4">
                                    <div class="timeline-marker bg-primary"></div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="mb-1">9:00 AM - Morning Lectures</h5>
                                        <p>Start the day with engaging lectures in our modern teaching facilities.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-item mb-3 position-relative ps-4">
                                    <div class="timeline-marker bg-primary"></div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="mb-1">12:00 PM - Lunch with Friends</h5>
                                        <p>Enjoy lunch at one of our many campus dining options or nearby cafes.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-item mb-3 position-relative ps-4">
                                    <div class="timeline-marker bg-primary"></div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="mb-1">2:00 PM - Study Session</h5>
                                        <p>Utilize our libraries and study spaces for group or individual learning.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-item position-relative ps-4">
                                    <div class="timeline-marker bg-primary"></div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="mb-1">5:00 PM - Club Activities</h5>
                                        <p>Participate in club meetings, sports, or other extracurricular activities.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Student Testimonials -->
                <div class="mt-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">What Our Students Say</h2>
                    
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                                    <img src="images/student1.jpg" alt="Sarah" class="rounded-circle mb-3" width="80">
                                    <p class="fst-italic mb-3">"The community at Wolverhampton is incredible. I've made friends for life and learned so much both in and out of lectures."</p>
                                    <h5 class="mb-1">Sarah, Computer Science</h5>
                                    <p class="small text-muted">Second Year Student</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                                    <img src="images/student2.jpg" alt="James" class="rounded-circle mb-3" width="80">
                                    <p class="fst-italic mb-3">"The campus facilities are top-notch, and there's always something happening. I've found it easy to balance my studies with social activities."</p>
                                    <h5 class="mb-1">James, Business Studies</h5>
                                    <p class="small text-muted">First Year Student</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
    
